Question: Does the food that is to the right of the coffee cup have light brown color?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n508733.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='RIGHT')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='coffee cup')
IMAGE1=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='food')
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the food?')
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'light brown' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
